            <para>
              <text>The heading to section 6 is amended by inserting <amend.in quote="1"><emphasis style="bold">direct Registrar regarding establishment of Crown holding accounts and</emphasis></amend.in> after <quote.in quote="1"><emphasis style="bold">may</emphasis></quote.in>.</text>
            </para>
