                        </label-para>
                        <label-para quote="1" skeleton="no">
                          <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes" quote="1">b</label>
                          <para>
                            <text>a person registered as a participant in respect of an activity listed in Part 1 of Schedule 4 who is described in the first column of Part B of the following table grants an interest or enters into a contract described in the second column:</text>
